{"tid":2155123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青年藏士巴拿行山杖被控 指警誘騙招認 向他稱義務律師「鑿你錢」","createTime":"2020-08-13T14:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T14:28:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a9d599478cc22d60da91266d91c3746d7a7122","tid":2155123,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:12:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/ZMMS4EQVPVEAROQWF2FZR3YLNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FZMMS4EQVPVEAROQWF2FZR3YLNI%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=75d7db52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FZMMS4EQVPVEAROQWF2FZR3YLNI%2F&h=838e5867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/ZMMS4EQVPVEAROQWF2FZR3YLNI/</a><br />\n<br />\n22歲青年去年9月於葵涌新都會廣場外被警截停，搜出士巴拿和行山杖，他聲稱用作自衛和保衛附近葵福路行人隧道的連儂牆。青年事後被控以管有攻擊性武器罪，案件今於西九龍裁判法院開審。辯方爭議被告的招認是在警方威迫誘導下作出，指警員曾向被告稱「義務律師10個有9個都係仆街，都係鑿你錢！」控方警員證人否認。"},{"pid":"fc508e016f31b635431792fe9cea0eed28924995","tid":2155123,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:13:51.000Z","msg":"多名手足明日裁決／判刑 包括其中1人已還押近半年<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2155070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2155070</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a3f04dbac6e2070ce6ffb6ebac41803bc6b50b03","tid":2155123,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42c7ffc77e2607d33d27b62991dfa00bd21da6c","tid":2155123,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma